name: Fatty Tee
description:
One of the hardest steps in loving your body can be reclaiming the words that have been used in the past to hurt you. Fat/Fatty have been words used in the past to insult us, but now have become our words we use to describe ourselves. Wear this shirt and show the world that you embrace your body in all of it's fabulous fatness. 

All designs are original hand lettered designs and screen printed on 100% cotton shirts.

name: Riots Not Diets Tee
description:
The media tries to keep us preoccupied with losing weight through harmful and often fruitless fad diets. Refuse to disappear or force your body to be more "acceptable". Reject Diet Culture and embrace the radical notion that your body doesn't need to change just because society thinks so.

All designs are original hand lettered designs and screen printed on 100% cotton shirts.

name: Decadent Tee
description:
Born from a love of all things extravagant, this tee was designed with a love of opulence in mind. When wearing this shirt you can declare your desire of all things decadent, including the decadence of soft supple flesh. 

All designs are original hand lettered designs and screen printed on 100% cotton shirts.
